descript.abstract: This data layer represents parcels for Columbia County, Wisconsin in 2012. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Columbia_Parcels_2012.gdb.
descript.purpose: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data
descript.supplinf: For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement.
